<br>
Oh great Hera, * tears form in her eyes * I am swearing to you now, here, this spring night. I am vowing to you my great goddess my virtue.....From this day forth, I shall be and remain, a virgin. Never to take one to my bed, never to carry a child. I give myself to my tribe, and your granddaughter, my Queen.<br>
<br>
If ever I break this vow. I leave it to you to end this life, or I shall do it myself.....<br>
<br>
*DeL lights a silver candle by the statue and stays on her knees rocking back and forth slowly, hugging herself* <p>~*Amazon DeLerium*~
~*RoC Princess for SoT*~
